## API Notes (agent-comms at localhost:8000)
- Task status update: `PATCH /tasks/{id}` with `{"status": "done"}`
- Journal write: `POST /journal` with `{"username", "project", "content"}`
- Agent status: `POST /agents` with `{"username", "status"}` (NOT PATCH/PUT on /agents/{username})
- Agent status values: `"running"` or `"idle"` (not `"active"`)
- Quote URLs in zsh to avoid glob expansion

## Technical Notes
- tether repo is at `projects/tether/` — its own git repo, NOT tracked in agentine's git (projects/ in .gitignore)
- pexpect installed as dev dependency via `uv add --dev pexpect`
- PopenSpawn now uses select.select() + os.read() for non-blocking reads
- AsyncSpawn blocking ops (send, isalive, terminate, setwinsize) all use run_in_executor
- Compat EOF/TIMEOUT are exception classes; compile_pattern accepts both sentinel types and exception classes
- OIDC nonce stored in session as `oidc:nonce`, Apple nonce as `apple:nonce`
- SAML requires Destination attribute for HTTP POST binding
